{
  "stem": "3757.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the-- were-- were partners-- they opened a big office in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the partners one day disappeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father left without a penny.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And even he had debts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had to sell my mother's jewelry and silver, and everything what was available.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so this are how I grew up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was your family religious?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very orthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With the orthodox Kazinczy Street shul",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back hundreds and hundreds of years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was in the Mizrachi Movement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was only in the Zionist organization, also from my early childhood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was much, much later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Germany was a very democratic country at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Hungary, I was aware of it, because in Hungary, there were so many political changes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were, I think, they were born anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In 19-- after the first world war, where my father was enrolled in the war, as I-- I don't know what he did.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think he did office work in the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after the war finished, in 1918, it became somehow the communist took over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a terrible time-- a terrible time, where there was no food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My-- luckily, my father was-- we were a lot of children-- he was able to provide us with-- with food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then the communist were conquered [BACKGROUND NOISE] by Horthy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then came the so-called White Terror.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then all my relatives from Hungary, from the country, they came up to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they thought in a big city, it's easier to escape somehow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember that I-- one of my cousins came home one day, and he was all blue and black.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And his fingers were all bloody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were captured by [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
